---
layout: layouts/base.njk
permalink: /contact/
slug: contact
chrome: minimal
heroAlign: left
callBar: true
includeFormJs: true
bodyClass: page--bofu
title: "Book a Free Discovery Call · TechBrot"
description: "Book a free 30-min discovery call with a Certified QuickBooks ProAdvisor — written fixed-fee scope in 3 business days, no pitch. Call (877) 751-5575."
hero:
  eyebrow: "Contact"
  heading: "Tell us about your books. We’ll do the rest."
  subheading: "Book a 30-minute discovery call. We’ll review where your books are, recommend the right engagement, and produce a written fixed-fee scope within 3 business days. If TechBrot isn’t the right fit, we’ll say so — and point you toward what is."
  actions:
    - { label: "Book the discovery call", href: "#contact-main", class: "btn--primary" }
    - { label: "Speak to a ProAdvisor", href: "tel:+18777515575", class: "btn--ghost" }
whyBullets:
  - "Certified QuickBooks ProAdvisors &times;4 (Online L2, Desktop, Enterprise, Payroll)"
  - "Fixed-fee scopes, written before any work begins"
  - "<a href=\"/legal/disclaimer/\">Independent ProAdvisor firm &mdash; not affiliated with Intuit Inc.</a>"
  - "We work in your QuickBooks file &mdash; you keep your data, always"
  - "Named operator, real accountability"
faq:
  - q: "What does the discovery call cost?"
    a: "Nothing. The 30-minute discovery call is complimentary, there&rsquo;s no hourly billing, and the written fixed-fee scope that follows is non-binding. Every engagement is priced from the canonical figures published on our <a href=\"/pricing/\">pricing page</a> &mdash; the scope you receive cites them."
  - q: "Will I get a sales pitch on the call?"
    a: "No. A Certified ProAdvisor reviews where your books are and recommends the right engagement &mdash; or none, if that&rsquo;s the honest answer. There&rsquo;s no commission for steering you anywhere, no follow-up sales sequence, and the call ends with a clear next step you&rsquo;re free to ignore."
  - q: "What if TechBrot isn&rsquo;t the right fit for my situation?"
    a: "We&rsquo;ll say so on the call and point you toward what does fit &mdash; including firms outside TechBrot when that&rsquo;s the honest answer. The discovery call is complimentary either way, and you keep everything you learned from it."
  - q: "Do you only work with businesses already on QuickBooks?"
    a: "No. If you&rsquo;re on Xero, Wave, other software, or spreadsheets, the discovery call covers whether a <a href=\"/quickbooks/migration/\">migration</a> or a fresh <a href=\"/quickbooks/setup/\">QuickBooks setup</a> makes sense &mdash; and if staying put is the right answer, we&rsquo;ll tell you that. New businesses with no accounting infrastructure yet are a regular starting point."
  - q: "How does pricing work after the discovery call?"
    a: "You get a written fixed-fee scope within 3 business days of the call. It binds us to the fee and the deliverables; it doesn&rsquo;t bind you. If genuinely new in-scope work emerges mid-engagement, we re-quote in writing before any of it happens &mdash; no scope creep, no hourly upcharges. Canonical figures live on the <a href=\"/pricing/\">pricing page</a>."
  - q: "Will I end up on a marketing list if I submit the form?"
    a: "No. Your details are used only to respond to this request &mdash; no marketing list, no sales follow-up sequence. The <a href=\"/legal/privacy-policy/\">privacy policy</a> covers exactly what happens to the information in the brief."
  - q: "My situation is urgent — can I skip the form?"
    a: "Yes. Call <a href=\"tel:+18777515575\" data-tb-event=\"phone_click\">(877) 751-5575</a>, Mon&ndash;Fri 9&nbsp;AM&ndash;6&nbsp;PM ET &mdash; a ProAdvisor answers during business hours. Or book directly on <a href=\"https://calendly.com/techbrot/discovery\" rel=\"noopener\">our calendar</a> without filling the form. Same operator, same outcome; the form just gets us the details before the call."
    phone: true
---
{#- CONTACT — endpoint type (founder 2026-06-17). Shared util-hero (404 treatment)
    + the form as the centerpiece below it. Discovery furniture stripped: no AI Q&A,
    no numbered process, no breadcrumb. Equity-GREEN: every baseline heading kept
    (h1 in the hero; "How to reach us…", "Send us your situation.", "If the form
    isn’t the right path." + the 4 alt h3s); #contact-promise (speakable target)
    preserved; schema lives in contact.11tydata.js (untouched). -#}

{% include "partials/util-hero.njk" %}

<section class="section section--alt" id="contact-main">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <header class="section__header">
      <p class="section__eyebrow" data-intent-headline>Discovery brief</p>
      <h2 class="section__heading" id="contact-main-heading">Send us your situation.</h2>
      <p class="section__lede" data-intent-lede>Six minutes. Six fields. We&rsquo;ll respond within one business day with discovery call slots and a sense of where we&rsquo;d start.</p>
    </header>
    <div class="contact-form-wrap">
      {%- set intakePrefix = "contact" %}
      {%- set intakeFormId = "contact-discovery-form" %}
      {%- set intakeIntent = "" %}
      {%- set intakeSourceType = "" %}
      {%- set intakeFunnelStage = "" %}
      {%- set intakeLegend = "What we should discuss" %}
      {%- set intakeNote = "Pick what fits. Pick more than one if more than one fits." %}
      {%- set intakeConsent = "I agree to be contacted by TechBrot regarding this inquiry." %}
      {%- set intakeSubmit = "Send the Discovery Brief" %}
      {%- set intakeReassurance = "Response within 1 business day. No marketing list. No sales follow-up sequence." %}
      {% include "partials/intake-form.njk" %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section" id="contact-promise-section">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <header class="section__header">
      <p class="section__eyebrow">Our response promise</p>
      <h2 class="section__heading">How to reach us &amp; what to expect</h2>
    </header>
    <p class="prose" id="contact-promise">Every discovery-brief submission gets a response from a Certified ProAdvisor within 1 business day. Discovery calls are scheduled within 3&ndash;5 business days, and written fixed-fee scopes are delivered within 3 business days of the call. Prefer to talk first? Call <a href="tel:{{ site.phone.e164 }}" data-tb-event="phone_click">(877) 751-5575</a>, Mon&ndash;Fri 9&nbsp;AM&ndash;6&nbsp;PM ET, or email <a href="mailto:{{ site.emails.hello }}">{{ site.emails.hello }}</a> &mdash; replied within 1 business day. If you&rsquo;d rather have the actual file looked at before anyone talks, start with the <a href="/quickbooks/file-review/?intent=file-review">free QuickBooks file review</a>. Canonical pricing for every engagement is published on the <a href="/pricing/">pricing page</a>.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--alt" id="contact-trust">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <header class="section__header">
      <p class="section__eyebrow">Before you decide</p>
      <h2 class="section__heading" id="contact-trust-heading">Why owners choose TechBrot</h2>
    </header>
    <ul class="checks-list">
      {%- for item in whyBullets %}
      <li>{{ item | safe }}</li>
      {%- endfor %}
    </ul>
    <div class="grid-2 stack-8">
      <article class="review-card">
        <h3>Direct contact</h3>
        <p class="review-card__fact"><strong>Phone:</strong> <a href="tel:{{ site.phone.e164 }}" data-tb-event="phone_click">+1 (877) 751-5575</a> &mdash; Mon&ndash;Fri, 9&nbsp;AM&ndash;6&nbsp;PM ET</p>
        <p class="review-card__fact"><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:{{ site.emails.hello }}">{{ site.emails.hello }}</a> &mdash; replied within 1 business day</p>
      </article>
      <article class="review-card">
        <h3>Headquartered</h3>
        <p class="review-card__fact">{{ site.legalName }}<br>{{ site.address.streetAddress }}<br>{{ site.address.addressLocality }}, {{ site.address.addressRegion }} {{ site.address.postalCode }}<br>United States</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section" id="contact-alt">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <header class="section__header">
      <p class="section__eyebrow">Other ways to connect</p>
      <h2 class="section__heading" id="contact-alt-heading">If the form isn&rsquo;t the right path.</h2>
    </header>
    <div class="grid-2">
      <article class="review-card">
        <h3>Schedule directly</h3>
        <p class="review-card__fact">Book a 30-minute discovery call on our calendar without filling the form. Same operator, same outcome.</p>
        <a class="review-card__link" href="https://calendly.com/techbrot/discovery" rel="noopener" data-cta="contact-alt-calendar">Open the calendar <span class="lnk-arrow" aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span></a>
      </article>
      <article class="review-card">
        <h3>Call us</h3>
        <p class="review-card__fact">Speak with a ProAdvisor directly during business hours. We answer the phone &mdash; this isn&rsquo;t routed through an offshore queue.</p>
        <a class="review-card__link" href="tel:{{ site.phone.e164 }}" data-tb-event="phone_click">+1 (877) 751-5575 <span class="lnk-arrow" aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span></a>
      </article>
      <article class="review-card">
        <h3>Partner inquiry</h3>
        <p class="review-card__fact">If you&rsquo;re an independent accounting practice interested in the operator network, the partner application form is the right path.</p>
        <a class="review-card__link" href="/partners/">Apply to the network <span class="lnk-arrow" aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span></a>
      </article>
      <article class="review-card">
        <h3>Press &amp; media</h3>
        <p class="review-card__fact">Journalists, podcast hosts, and event organizers can reach our media contact directly.</p>
        <a class="review-card__link" href="mailto:{{ site.emails.press }}">{{ site.emails.press }} <span class="lnk-arrow" aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span></a>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--alt" id="contact-faq">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <header class="section__header">
      <p class="section__eyebrow">Before you send it</p>
      <h2 class="section__heading">The questions buyers actually ask.</h2>
    </header>
    <div class="faq__list">
      {%- for item in faq %}
      <div class="faq__item">
        <h3 class="faq__question">
          <button class="faq__trigger" type="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="contact-faq-a{{ loop.index }}">{{ item.q | safe }}</button>
        </h3>
        <div class="faq__answer" id="contact-faq-a{{ loop.index }}" data-open="false">
          <p>{{ item.a | safe }}</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      {%- endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
window.TB_INTENT_MAP = {{ intents.intents | dump | safe }};
window.TB_LOOKUPS = {{ intents.lookups | dump | safe }};
</script>
